# Shared Libraries

The `shared/` directory contains libraries and utilities that are used across multiple workspaces in the project.

## SDK

The Software Development Kit (SDK) in [shared/sdk](mdc:shared/sdk) provides core functionality and interfaces for interacting with Zeiro services.

## CLI

The Command Line Interface (CLI) in [shared/cli](mdc:shared/cli) provides tools for developers to interact with Zeiro from the command line.

The CLI can be installed locally with:
```bash
yarn install-cli
```
